            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>Initial public release</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Watches <strong>Claude Desktop</strong> windows and
                        <strong>Claude Code</strong> running in Terminal.app
                        for usage-limit banners.</li>
                    <li>Reads the reset time Claude reports and waits
                        precisely for it, then types <code>continue</code>
                        and sends it automatically.</li>
                    <li>Tracks multiple conversations independently, each
                        on its own timer.</li>
                    <li>Lives in the menu bar, launches at login, and keeps
                        a local activity log you can inspect from the
                        menu.</li>
                </ul>
